1
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:18,280
[2010]

2
00:00:26,230 --> 00:00:27,760
Professor Geng came over a few days ago.

3
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,320
Prof.

4
00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:29,620
Come in.

5
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:31,810
Come in.

6
00:00:38,390 --> 00:00:40,450
These files have been reclassified.

7
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:42,430
These are the research notes.

8
00:00:42,430 --> 00:00:43,220
All questionable items

9
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:44,220
have been marked.

10
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,380
Please have a look.

11
00:00:47,110 --> 00:00:48,840
I have read the book you gave me.

12
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,480
These are the reading notes.

13
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,720
Okay, put them there.

14
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:54,520
Go back early.

15
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:10,350
Is this

16
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:13,030
the Jiang Hansheng you mentioned before?

17
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,200
Jealous?

18
00:01:21,950 --> 00:01:23,840
Having such a remarkable student

19
00:01:24,710 --> 00:01:25,710
is a rare blessing

20
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,230
in my life.

21
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:30,940
But he

22
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,590
has a weakness,

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,600
too eager for quick success.

24
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,479
Why is that?

25
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,420
Ever since he got

26
00:01:38,450 --> 00:01:40,590
the authority
to handle cases independently,

27
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:42,560
he has accepted all kinds of cases.

28
00:01:43,229 --> 00:01:44,400
He works desperately.

29
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,070
To himself,

30
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:46,520
and to the enemy,

31
00:01:47,150 --> 00:01:49,000
he keeps

32
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,330
a hidden ruthlessness.

33
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,789
That ruthlessness

34
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:54,870
makes me

35
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:56,710
worried.

36
00:01:58,759 --> 00:01:59,920
Why is it like this?

37
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:00,760
I asked him

38
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:02,780
why he works

39
00:02:02,810 --> 00:02:03,920
so desperately.

40
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,510
Was he for the truth

41
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,360
or for credit?

42
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,710
Do you know what he said?

43
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:12,890
For promotion?

44
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,590
He said

45
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,800
he did so

46
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,470
to fulfill a wish.

47
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:31,950
Senior,

48
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,190
I know you well.

49
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,810
You have a broad perspective.

50
00:02:35,829 --> 00:02:37,010
You must be unsatisfied

51
00:02:37,010 --> 00:02:38,180
with his answer.

52
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,360
Frankly speaking,

53
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,240
his

54
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,310
edge

55
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,190
and ability

56
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,590
are top-notch.

57
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:50,880
But his personality

58
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,370
is not good enough.

59
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:57,000
Don't jump the gun.

60
00:02:58,370 --> 00:03:00,300
Wait until something big happens.

61
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:01,700
Then we'll see.

62
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:26,710
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

63
00:04:27,110 --> 00:04:29,470
[Episode 11]

64
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,120
He's gone.

65
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,230
We found his phone

66
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:34,310
and the tracker on his boutonniere
in the car.

67
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:34,950
What?

68
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,070
He's gone?

69
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,950
How could he be gone?

70
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:43,270
But the one who showed up
that day wasn't Qi Yan.

71
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:44,600
It was his subordinate.

72
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:46,000
Yao Weihai

73
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,070
didn't give an order in time

74
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,310
to rescue Hansheng.

75
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,750
That was the only chance to catch

76
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:53,190
the crime syndicate of the 8/17 Case.

77
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:54,830
If we missed it,

78
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:57,840
all our previous efforts would be in vain.

79
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,430
He must make

80
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:02,030
a choice that benefits
the overall situation.

81
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,690
I know it.

82
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:05,610
But…

83
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:09,560
It's about to pass the golden 72 hours.

84
00:05:10,450 --> 00:05:11,570
If we still can't find…

85
00:05:11,570 --> 00:05:12,430
Yao Weihai!

86
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:24,720
Leader Yao, then we will go look
for him first.

87
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:32,600
Senior,

88
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,040
it's my fault.

89
00:05:36,870 --> 00:05:37,680
Where is he?

90
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,360
Where is he?

91
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,270
Give my student back.

92
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:46,930
Give him back to me.

93
00:05:48,350 --> 00:05:50,080
Give him back!

94
00:05:53,010 --> 00:05:54,870
We've been trying our best
to look for him.

95
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:55,950
Did you find him?

96
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:59,390
How did you promise me back then?

97
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,270
You said you would

98
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:02,390
guarantee his safety.

99
00:06:02,490 --> 00:06:03,340
Where is he?

100
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,270
Tell me, where is he?

101
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,310
I'm sorry.

102
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:17,270
You bastard!

103
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,890
Where is the pocket watch?

104
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,040
Did he have the pocket watch with him?

105
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,100
What pocket watch?

106
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:42,210
[The sixth day
after Jiang Hansheng was kidnapped]

107
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,030
What are you waiting for?

108
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,370
Waiting for your friends to save you?

109
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,000
They won't be here.

110
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,630
They can't find this place at all.

111
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,120
They abandoned you.

112
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:13,370
Officer Jiang, have you realized

113
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,190
who your real friend is?

114
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:20,920
Me.

115
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,430
I am your real friend.

116
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:27,490
As long as you accept me as a friend,

117
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:31,820
just say,

118
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:34,150
"I am your friend",

119
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:38,390
and I will let you die comfortably.

120
00:08:43,659 --> 00:08:46,190
The tracker of the pocket watch
is activated.

121
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:48,680
Let’s go!

122
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,640
Give me the pocket watch.

123
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,040
Give me the pocket watch.

124
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:04,730
Officer Jiang.

125
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,670
Jiang Hansheng,

126
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,340
I changed my mind.

127
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:13,240
I won't let you die.

128
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,960
I will make your life a living hell.

129
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,510
What do you want?

130
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,040
You want this, right?

131
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,800
You want this, right?

132
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,200
You want it?

133
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,760
You want her?

134
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,000
You want your girl, right?

135
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:35,550
You will never

136
00:09:37,950 --> 00:09:39,640
get her.

137
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:54,750
Six days.

138
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:58,120
After a full six days,

139
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:02,630
Yao Weihai finally found

140
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,120
Hansheng in an abandoned warehouse.

141
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:07,380
When he was sent into the operating room,

142
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,630
the doctors told me

143
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,960
that multiple organs

144
00:10:12,610 --> 00:10:13,360
in his body

145
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,780
were already showing signs of failure.

146
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,840
They let me brace myself.

147
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:23,750
He never mentioned

148
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:26,000
how he survived those six days.

149
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,390
I have no idea.

150
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,200
What I do know is that

151
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,780
although Hansheng received
an award and praise

152
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,510
for this arrest,

153
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:42,940
his treatment lasted for a full two years.

154
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,910
What's up?

155
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,910
Can you help me dry my hair?

156
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:33,200
What are you looking at?

157
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,270
You.

158
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,680
Do you have something to say?

159
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:24,790
Is your name

160
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,720
Jiang Hansheng?

161
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:32,150
Yes, it is.

162
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,280
You wouldn't lie to me, would you?

163
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:49,810
I didn't lie to you.

164
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,770
Did you really not lie to me?

165
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:59,220
Then what about

166
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:02,030
a close call

167
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,030
you told me?

168
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:12,930
Jiang Hansheng.

169
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:15,030
Why?

170
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,130
Those things five years ago

171
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,790
have nothing to do with you.

172
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,840
Why did you do that?

173
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:32,960
Did Prof...

174
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:43,800
Jiang Hansheng.

175
00:14:46,790 --> 00:14:47,600
Why?

176
00:14:50,790 --> 00:14:51,440
Zhou Jin,

177
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:54,000
that’s my job.

178
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,320
It has nothing to do with you.

179
00:14:57,030 --> 00:14:57,830
You're lying.

180
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,320
At that time,

181
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:05,240
I didn't even remember you.

182
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:13,960
Don't cry.

183
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:21,790
Do you like me?

184
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,840
Yes.

185
00:15:26,910 --> 00:15:28,550
Since when?

186
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:32,870
Zhou Jin,

187
00:15:34,150 --> 00:15:34,750
I love you.

188
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,480
When I first met you,

189
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:42,280
I wanted to have you.

190
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,240
You're late.

191
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:44,920
I had to deal with something
before coming out.

192
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:47,030
How long do I have to wait?

193
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,840
What do you mean? Are you rushing me?

194
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:49,550
Sir.

195
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:50,550
It's been five years.

196
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:51,790
Can't I rush you?

197
00:16:51,820 --> 00:16:52,840
I haven't even scolded you yet.

198
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,840
Do you know why I'm late?

199
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:54,840
Why should I care?

200
00:16:55,510 --> 00:16:56,840
Is Heipi your man?

201
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:59,000
He was beaten badly

202
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:01,120
and thrown at the door
of the narcotics team.

203
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,580
He kept calling for Cheng.

204
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,329
If I weren't there for a meeting,

205
00:17:04,329 --> 00:17:06,460
you'd have another mess on your hands.

206
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,349
He has nothing to do with me.

207
00:17:08,349 --> 00:17:09,550
He has nothing to do with you?

208
00:17:09,550 --> 00:17:10,500
What about Huang Song?

209
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:11,810
What about Lai San?

210
00:17:11,829 --> 00:17:12,869
Get it straight.

211
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:14,650
It's Lai San's own crime of killing a man.

212
00:17:14,650 --> 00:17:15,910
I asked Huang Song to help him
dispose of the body

213
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:17,970
so that you guys could find it sooner.

214
00:17:18,349 --> 00:17:19,480
Why are you yelling?

215
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:25,130
When will Lai San be sentenced?

216
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,170
I don't know.

217
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,960
He has the gun you handed in.

218
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:42,150
He'll be sentenced sooner or later.

219
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:43,550
He has been involved in other cases.

220
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:45,550
They have to be dealt with together.

221
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,830
What did you explain about the gun?

222
00:17:47,830 --> 00:17:49,160
Fished it out of the sea.

223
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:50,270
Awesome.

224
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,790
You guys went into the sea
to fish out a gun.

225
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:54,520
Your subordinate, Huang Song,

226
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,890
might have to serve a few years too.

227
00:17:57,340 --> 00:17:59,470
He stole drugs and sold them secretly,

228
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:02,080
breaking the rules of the gang.

229
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,110
By going to prison,

230
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:04,440
he gets to keep his life.

231
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:09,160
How about you?

232
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:12,030
Me?

233
00:18:12,030 --> 00:18:12,630
Of course.

234
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:13,760
I want to go home.

235
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:14,920
Will you approve it?

236
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:17,970
Alright.

237
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:18,790
Just kidding.

238
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,400
Did Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng

239
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:27,400
cause any trouble for you recently?

240
00:18:27,600 --> 00:18:29,510
As the ex, I'm the trouble itself.

241
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,870
As you said,

242
00:18:33,330 --> 00:18:35,660
I transferred her away from the 8/17 Case.

243
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:37,350
She must be furious.

244
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,720
She has already

245
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,450
cut you into pieces in her mind.

246
00:18:40,870 --> 00:18:41,760
I don't care,

247
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,450
as long as you're okay with it.

248
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:49,930
Alright.

249
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:51,360
Let's talk business.

250
00:18:52,270 --> 00:18:53,720
They will restock soon,

251
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:55,640
transporting a large batch of meth
from the Jin-Hai Line.

252
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,680
He Wu is taking it very seriously.

253
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,960
It must be a big deal.

254
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:01,610
Time and place?

255
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,060
Not confirmed yet.

256
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:04,440
However,

257
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:06,740
it's said that Old Scorpion
will personally supervise this time.

258
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:08,800
So, they are acting very cautiously.

259
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:12,400
Find a way to get close to Old Scorpion.

260
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:13,880
He Wu will definitely

261
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,140
be short of hands then.

262
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:16,110
Without Lai San,

263
00:19:16,310 --> 00:19:17,750
I am confident I can make him choose me.

264
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:18,550
It has to be me.

265
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,030
It's been five years.

266
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,470
We finally got the business

267
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,640
of the Jin-Hai Line.

268
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:32,120
Old Scorpion has been hiding
for so many years

269
00:19:32,310 --> 00:19:33,710
and has finally shown up.

270
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:34,920
Yes.

271
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:37,830
This is our only chance.

272
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,920
After this,

273
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:41,720
I can go home.

274
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,610
Does He Wu trust you?

275
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:48,920
Don't worry about that.

276
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:49,920
I have my own ways.

277
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,120
Jiang Cheng, listen,

278
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,540
don't do anything out of bounds

279
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:55,060
to get promoted.

280
00:19:56,550 --> 00:19:57,350
Out of bounds?

281
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:59,200
Tell me, what are the bounds?

282
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,040
Where are they?

283
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:02,040
What does it mean to be out of bounds?

284
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,560
What are you doing? Defiant?

285
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:22,790
Yes, I don't buy it.

286
00:20:23,790 --> 00:20:24,270
Yao.

287
00:20:25,230 --> 00:20:25,960
Look at this.

288
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:26,990
During the last deal,

289
00:20:26,990 --> 00:20:28,420
I was shot by our man.

290
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:30,250
I almost died in the hospital.

291
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,170
And here.

292
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,880
When I was in prison,

293
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:33,880
I got slashed.

294
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:34,830
And here.

295
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:35,830
Look.

296
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:37,210
I have more scars.

297
00:20:37,210 --> 00:20:39,010
Do you want to see them one by one?

298
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:39,830
Tell me,

299
00:20:39,830 --> 00:20:41,560
at what time was I out of bounds?

300
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,710
I had no parents since I was young.

301
00:20:46,710 --> 00:20:48,280
The Zhou family raised me.

302
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:51,150
They are the ones
who care about me the most.

303
00:20:51,630 --> 00:20:53,250
Every time I couldn't hold on,

304
00:20:53,250 --> 00:20:54,310
as long as I thought of them,

305
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:55,680
thought of my family waiting
for me at home,

306
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,880
I didn't even dare to die.

307
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,010
I could only hold on.

308
00:20:58,310 --> 00:20:59,030
But now?

309
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:00,480
Yao, tell me,

310
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,790
what have I become?

311
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,820
How about this?

312
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:06,860
You take the gun

313
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,960
and shoot me dead.

314
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:09,240
I will thank you.

315
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,830
Really.

316
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,100
I know Zhou Jin's marriage

317
00:21:20,470 --> 00:21:21,930
makes you uncomfortable.

318
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,610
But you are not a teenager anymore.

319
00:21:25,330 --> 00:21:27,240
This is the critical moment
of the planned round-up.

320
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:28,680
You can't mess it up

321
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:29,420
just because of Zhou Jin.

322
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,550
Zhou Chuan died!

323
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:33,290
That's why I volunteered to do this.

324
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,240
You were right about one thing.

325
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:47,560
If someone wants to accomplish something,

326
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:49,640
he must have faith.

327
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,270
This is

328
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,270
my faith.

329
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,510
Are you sure?

330
00:21:56,330 --> 00:22:03,330
[2012]

331
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:57,830
Yes.

332
00:21:59,310 --> 00:22:01,110
I only have two requests for you.

333
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:01,880
First,

334
00:22:02,270 --> 00:22:03,730
stay firm with your faith.

335
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:04,350
Second,

336
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:05,770
stay alive.

337
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:06,790
Yes.

338
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:09,200
I promise to complete the mission.

339
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,310
I

340
00:22:15,160 --> 00:22:17,360
can't let my family shed tears anymore.

341
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:57,830
Isn't this a gift from Zhou?

342
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,240
Don't forget.

343
00:23:14,360 --> 00:23:17,250
Even if everything has changed
in the past five years,

344
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:18,400
you're still a cop.

345
00:23:31,230 --> 00:23:31,880
Watch out!

346
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,270
Xiao Mao?

347
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:45,450
Cheng.

348
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:48,320
Didn't you stop being a cop?

349
00:23:48,610 --> 00:23:49,740
If Boss He finds out,

350
00:23:50,110 --> 00:23:51,400
you'll be dead meat.

351
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,410
Did he tell you to follow me?

352
00:23:54,680 --> 00:23:55,240
Speak!

353
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:58,280
Yes.

354
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:01,640
Cheng,

355
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,200
can you let me go?

356
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,830
I didn't see anything.

357
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:06,000
I didn't see anything.

358
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:07,000
Let me go, please.

359
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:08,550
Turn yourself in,

360
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:09,240
right now.

361
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:10,500
I can't, Cheng.

362
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:12,960
Turning myself in means killing me.

363
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:14,110
Let me go.

364
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,700
I won't say anything.

365
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:16,590
Not a word.

366
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:17,400
Cheng.

367
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:18,110
Xiao Mao,

368
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:19,410
don't force me.

369
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:22,550
I've treated you like
my brother for so many years.

370
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:23,680
Or,

371
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,680
don't you think about your brother?

372
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,350
Okay.

373
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,240
Cheng,

374
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,570
I'll listen to you.

375
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,050
I'll turn myself in.

376
00:24:37,050 --> 00:24:38,180
I won't say a word.

377
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:39,810
I'll turn myself in.

378
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:44,960
Cheng,

379
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,170
don't blame me.

380
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,920
You brought this on yourself.
You're a cop.

381
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:48,950
It's either you or me.

382
00:24:48,950 --> 00:24:49,880
I have no choice.

383
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:15,840
Jiang Cheng,

384
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:16,880
let go.

385
00:25:17,310 --> 00:25:18,110
Let go!

386
00:25:27,110 --> 00:25:28,680
Don't worry, he won't die.

387
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,400
Can you be more careful?

388
00:25:31,750 --> 00:25:33,150
Did you bring handcuffs?

389
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:40,350
I was always curious before.

390
00:25:40,350 --> 00:25:41,240
Every time you see me,

391
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,300
did you bring them?

392
00:25:42,590 --> 00:25:43,880
Cut the crap, hurry up.

393
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,960
I'll leave the rest to you.

394
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,030
Didn't you say you could
handle your subordinates?

395
00:26:01,030 --> 00:26:02,020
You were careless?

396
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:02,500
So,

397
00:26:02,530 --> 00:26:03,860
what other tricks do you have
to win people over?

398
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:04,860
Teach me quickly.

399
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:07,200
Is Dahua reliable?

400
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,540
Dahua is different from them.

401
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:10,990
He's an orphan,

402
00:26:11,010 --> 00:26:12,720
and only needs to feed himself.

403
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:14,000
He has no weaknesses

404
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,560
and no blood on his hands.

405
00:26:15,820 --> 00:26:16,880
He's kind at heart.

406
00:26:17,970 --> 00:26:20,210
Two years ago, Lai San forced him
to stab someone.

407
00:26:20,210 --> 00:26:21,070
But Dahua would rather jump
into the river,

408
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:21,920
than doing so.

409
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:25,190
He seems to consider you
his savior, right?

410
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,240
He was so naive,

411
00:26:27,240 --> 00:26:28,240
so I brought him along.

412
00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:30,040
Otherwise, he might get killed.

413
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:32,480
Dahua knows this very well himself.

414
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:38,040
Then how will you go back?

415
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:39,960
What else can I do?

416
00:26:40,830 --> 00:26:41,680
Wish me luck.

417
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:42,890
Jiang Cheng!

418
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:44,560
I know.

419
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:46,790
One wrong step will kill me.

420
00:26:47,590 --> 00:26:48,350
Don't worry.

421
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:50,400
I want to come back alive.

422
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:51,990
Until I contact you,

423
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,540
we should not meet.

424
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,550
If I die,

425
00:26:58,550 --> 00:26:59,720
collect my body.

426
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:17,050
That's Professor Jiang's car, right?

427
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:20,770
Yes, Professor Jiang.

428
00:27:30,220 --> 00:27:30,880
Oh my.

429
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,720
Why did it rain so heavily
all of a sudden?

430
00:27:35,720 --> 00:27:36,980
Don't you have a class?

431
00:27:37,030 --> 00:27:38,790
It's fine. I have time,

432
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,480
and this case…

433
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,000
Senior.

434
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,080
Umbrella.

435
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,000
Well, if you told me earlier

436
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,860
that Professor Jiang
was dropping you off,

437
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:49,480
I wouldn't have come down to pick you up.

438
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,660
In the past, you could chase a petty thief

439
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,740
for eight blocks.

440
00:27:51,830 --> 00:27:53,200
Now that you're married,

441
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:54,420
you can't even open a car door

442
00:27:54,420 --> 00:27:55,550
or hold an umbrella.

443
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:57,680
Why do you talk so much?

444
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,790
Professor Jiang, control your wife.

445
00:27:58,790 --> 00:28:00,590
She's bullying the vulnerable.

446
00:28:00,790 --> 00:28:01,400
Sorry.

447
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,260
I'm afraid I'm one of the vulnerable too.

448
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:05,480
See?

449
00:28:05,870 --> 00:28:06,590
Fine.

450
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,030
I've had enough of your romantic behavior.

451
00:28:08,030 --> 00:28:08,760
I'm leaving.

452
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:10,840
Let's go.

453
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:15,330
What do you want to know

454
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:17,400
about this case?

455
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:19,680
Regarding Zhao Xiaoyu's case,

456
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,280
I'd like to ask your opinion.

457
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:23,200
Are you really asking for my opinion?

458
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:23,960
The way you ask

459
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,310
is like my high school teacher

460
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,720
making me recite a text.

461
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:30,590
I genuinely want to seek advice
from Officer Zhou.

462
00:28:30,970 --> 00:28:32,110
When you were in high school,

463
00:28:32,110 --> 00:28:33,340
did you dislike reciting texts?

464
00:28:33,340 --> 00:28:34,620
Of course.

465
00:28:35,450 --> 00:28:36,850
A top student like you

466
00:28:36,870 --> 00:28:38,600
cannot understand a poor student's pain.

467
00:28:38,600 --> 00:28:40,680
When I was in school,
I even went to tutoring.

468
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,160
The tutor I found

469
00:28:42,180 --> 00:28:43,340
was my mom's classmate,

470
00:28:43,340 --> 00:28:44,410
a total tyrant.

471
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,750
If I recited wrong,

472
00:28:46,090 --> 00:28:48,550
she would hit my palms
with a remote control.

473
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:49,480
Did it hurt?

474
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,550
Of course it did.

475
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:52,480
She said pain could teach me a lesson.

476
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,360
You're much better.

477
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:55,030
Your students must be very happy.

478
00:28:55,030 --> 00:28:57,230
If you had been in Zhizi Alley back then,

479
00:28:57,550 --> 00:28:59,310
I definitely would have
asked you for tutoring.

480
00:28:59,310 --> 00:28:59,880
Zhou Jin.

481
00:29:00,410 --> 00:29:00,900
Here.

482
00:29:00,670 --> 00:29:03,800
♪ I should never have let you bear this ♪

483
00:29:07,630 --> 00:29:11,640
♪ I always want to give you
everything I have ♪

484
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,040
Hansheng.

485
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:10,760
What's up?

486
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:12,400
Let's go.

487
00:29:12,550 --> 00:29:14,480
I have some new ideas for you today.

488
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:18,760
♪ If only it could win your heart,
even for a moment ♪

489
00:29:19,340 --> 00:29:22,410
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

490
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:26,560
♪ They're so free ♪

491
00:29:28,810 --> 00:29:31,880
♪ How can I tell you ♪

492
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:35,530
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

493
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:39,030
♪ I am sure to ♪

494
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:42,610
♪ Walk with you ♪

495
00:29:43,630 --> 00:29:47,110
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

496
00:29:47,130 --> 00:29:51,260
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

497
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:53,500
♪ At the crossroad ♪

498
00:29:53,530 --> 00:29:56,900
♪ To the left or right ♪

499
00:29:57,900 --> 00:30:01,820
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

500
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:15,830
You two take a look.

501
00:30:15,830 --> 00:30:17,830
I'll keep checking the statements.

502
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:24,550
They were sitting here that day.

503
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:27,180
Zhao Xiaoyu was

504
00:30:27,210 --> 00:30:28,340
sitting right here.

505
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:39,950
What are your thoughts?

506
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:42,650
We can do the crime scene simulation,

507
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:44,270
a compulsory course at the police academy.

508
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,830
I can put myself in Zhao Xiaoyu's shoes

509
00:30:45,830 --> 00:30:48,690
and reenact the encounter
with the killer that day.

510
00:30:48,690 --> 00:30:50,000
Do you remember the witness statements?

511
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:50,600
Of course.

512
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:51,720
Okay.

513
00:30:52,110 --> 00:30:53,910
Let's start the simulation now.

514
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,020
You observe me.

515
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:06,070
Stop me if there's any problem.

516
00:31:06,310 --> 00:31:06,680
Okay.

517
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,340
Take your time.

518
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,400
Xiaoyu,

519
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:41,110
let's have another drink.

520
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:00,740
Xi,

521
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:03,310
I'm not feeling well.

522
00:32:03,670 --> 00:32:04,830
I want to get some fresh air.

523
00:32:04,830 --> 00:32:06,530
What's wrong? Are you okay?

524
00:32:06,750 --> 00:32:07,590
I'm fine.

525
00:32:08,110 --> 00:32:09,640
Can you manage by yourself?

526
00:32:09,860 --> 00:32:10,650
Don't worry.

527
00:32:11,570 --> 00:32:13,060
Xi, let's have a drink.

528
00:32:13,270 --> 00:32:13,960
Okay.

529
00:32:29,760 --> 00:32:31,110
Hey, gorgeous.

530
00:32:31,750 --> 00:32:32,680
Have a drink.

531
00:33:30,140 --> 00:33:30,990
Are you okay?

532
00:33:49,030 --> 00:33:50,590
Come with me.

533
00:33:54,350 --> 00:33:55,400
Now?

534
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:00,370
What are you afraid of?

535
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,960
This killer is so bold.

536
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:18,679
In this environment,

537
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:20,190
he blatantly

538
00:34:20,210 --> 00:34:21,469
took Zhao Xiaoyu away.

539
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:23,230
Any new thoughts?

540
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:25,370
This is a provocation.

541
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:29,710
A copycat

542
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:31,440
usually takes

543
00:34:31,880 --> 00:34:33,070
his relative,

544
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,110
his friend,

545
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:36,290
or his admirer as the model.

546
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:39,480
As for the killer of
the Huaiguang Case, Qi Yan,

547
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:40,360
did the task force

548
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,800
check his family background

549
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,130
or social connections?

550
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:43,960
Of course.

551
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,600
But we found nothing.

552
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:46,960
We only know his name?

553
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,960
Before he showed up,

554
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:53,550
we had nothing but a profile

555
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:54,880
and his DNA.

556
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,110
I only knew his name

557
00:34:57,540 --> 00:34:59,790
when he told us.

558
00:35:01,590 --> 00:35:03,760
The task force, according to this name,

559
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:06,320
along with my descriptions
and profiling report,

560
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,880
deployed a large number
of grass-roots police forces

561
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:09,760
to conduct interviews and investigations

562
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,670
to further verify his identity.

563
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:14,110
But it all came to nothing.

564
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,480
Crime Research Lab

565
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,230
intended to use Qi Yan

566
00:35:17,230 --> 00:35:18,760
as a typical case study.

567
00:35:19,760 --> 00:35:21,150
However, the lack of his family background

568
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,590
and personal experience

569
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:25,370
prevented this project
from moving forward.

570
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:29,960
Is it possible

571
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:32,800
that Qi Yan isn't his real name?

572
00:35:34,590 --> 00:35:36,630
He didn't plan on letting me return alive.

573
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:37,440
There was no need to lie

574
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:38,840
to a dying man.

575
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,280
Let's go back.

576
00:35:49,070 --> 00:35:50,730
But there's one more question

577
00:35:51,230 --> 00:35:52,560
that I can't figure out.

578
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,110
Tell me.

579
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,880
Usually, copycat crimes are

580
00:35:58,150 --> 00:36:00,000
committed due to a lack of creativity

581
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,330
or a lack of experience.

582
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:03,920
That's why they need to copy others.

583
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:07,030
And the results are often clumsy.

584
